      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Drizzle <strong>olive oil </strong>over both sides of the <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong> and add them to the pan</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? You may need to do this in batches!</p>",
