      "instruction": "<p>Cover the mushrooms with a smaller, heavy-based pan and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once beginning to soften, turn the mushrooms so they are stem-side up and add a heavy weight (e.g. several cans) to the pan on top</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min further or until most of the moisture has been released</p><p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat and set aside</p>",
